OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRain will
OL,6,Fclear away south during this evening.
OL,7,FThen the rest of the night will be dry
OL,8,Fwith clear periods and a few light
OL,9,Fshowers. Cold with a frost in
OL,10,Fsheltered rural areas as the fresh
OL,11,Fnortherly wind eases.
OL,12,
OL,13,CMonday:FIsolated showers at first
OL,14,Fotherwise a dry day with some bright
OL,15,For sunny spells. Cloud increasing from
OL,16,Flate afternoon with patchy evening
OL,17,Frain as the southwesterly breeze
OL,18,Ffreshens.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
