OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FEarly
OL,6,Frain on Tuesday then sunny spells and
OL,7,Fshowers. Rather cold and unsettled
OL,8,FWednesday with scattered heavy
OL,9,Fshowers, the showers dying out through
OL,10,FThursday. Chance of overnight frosts.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
